\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 27, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104byl1665703025171.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/byl1665703025171.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/byl1665703025171.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"byl1665703025171\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Derived Entity\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Derived Entity is a Development Object that references and inherits from a Modeled Entity. It can be a subobject of a Modeled Entity (in which case it is known as a Subtype Entity), or of a Component or Modeled Component.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"byl1665703025171__section_kdq_1xp_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d150902e51\">Characteristics</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"byl1665703025171__table_d10487e1_d10488e1_d10489e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"byl1665703025171__table_d10487e1_d10488e1_d10489e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristic</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"byl1665703025171__table_d10487e1_d10488e1_d10489e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byl1665703025171__table_d10487e1_d10488e1_d10489e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byl1665703025171__table_d10487e1_d10488e1_d10489e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"byl1665703025171__image_a32_2xp_lwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/component_entity_modeled2_28bfc407b71b2e52dcf4790acd6d9797.png?_LANG=enus\"/></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byl1665703025171__table_d10487e1_d10488e1_d10489e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byl1665703025171__table_d10487e1_d10488e1_d10489e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ent</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byl1665703025171__table_d10487e1_d10488e1_d10489e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byl1665703025171__table_d10487e1_d10488e1_d10489e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byl1665703025171__table_d10487e1_d10488e1_d10489e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byl1665703025171__table_d10487e1_d10488e1_d10489e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tza1665702561698.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tza1665702561698.html\" title=\"A Modeled Entity is an Entity that defines a logical data aggregation at an abstract level. It is used to model the default properties and code of an entity, so that the Entity can be referenced and inherited by derived entities in components.\">Modeled Entity</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ifc1665702608950.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifc1665702608950.html\" title=\"A Component is a Main Development Object that defines an executable part of an application. It defines the data structure used to access data, the layout (if applicable) used to present it, and the actions used to modify, validate, and store data.\">Component</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vfj1665703025321.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vfj1665703025321.html\" title=\"A Modeled Component is a Component that can be used to create derived components, which inherit the component-level properties, code containers, and constants from the modeled component.\">Modeled Component</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byl1665703025171__table_d10487e1_d10488e1_d10489e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byl1665703025171__table_d10487e1_d10488e1_d10489e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lym1665702585074.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lym1665702585074.html\" title=\"A Field is a Development Object that represents a unit of data in an Entity. This could represent a column in a DBMS table or data that is not stored in the database, such as a derived field or a user interface control. Its associated properties define the way it is stored, its GUI representation, and default behavior.\">Field</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vuv1665702701508.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vuv1665702701508.html\" title=\"A Key is a Development Object that designates a field or combination of fields as a Primary Key, Candidate Key, or Index.\">Key</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xtb1665702702029.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xtb1665702702029.html\" title=\"A Relationship is a Development Object that represents an association between one entity and another. It specifies the primary or candidate keys to be used in maintaining the association, as well as the delete constraints to be used when deleting occurrences in the related entities.\">Relationship</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cny1665702550298.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cny1665702550298.html\" title=\"A Code Container is a type of Property that holds code, such as ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers, operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout.\">Code Container</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byl1665703025171__table_d10487e1_d10488e1_d10489e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byl1665703025171__table_d10487e1_d10488e1_d10489e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uqv1665702561461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uqv1665702561461.html\" title=\"An Entity is an abstract data type that defines a logical data aggregation and its associated default characteristics and behavior. It may be mapped to a table in a DBMS, and is most frequently used to represent the application data, but it can also represent transient data, a collection of controls, or constant data.\">Entity</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byl1665703025171__table_d10487e1_d10488e1_d10489e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byl1665703025171__table_d10487e1_d10488e1_d10489e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cnq1665702702174.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cnq1665702702174.html\" title=\"A Subtype Entity specializes a Modeled Entity (also known as the Supertype Entity). It is used to define a data set (or subset) for a special purpose, but that can be stored in the same database table as its Supertype.\">Subtype Entity</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xyt1665703024880.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xyt1665703024880.html\" title=\"A Derived Component Entity is a Development Object that references and inherits from a Modeled Entity. It has a Component or Modeled Component as parent object. It is used for the component's database I/O, data presentation, and inter-component communication.\">Derived Component Entity</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byl1665703025171__table_d10487e1_d10488e1_d10489e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byl1665703025171__table_d10487e1_d10488e1_d10489e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byl1665703025171__table_d10487e1_d10488e1_d10489e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byl1665703025171__table_d10487e1_d10488e1_d10489e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">ent:<var class=\"keyword varname\">SupertypeEntityName</var>/ent:<var class=\"keyword varname\">SubtypeEntityName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">cpt:<var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var>/ent:<var class=\"keyword varname\">EntityName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"byl1665703025171__section_xx3_fxp_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d150902e330\">Specialization</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"byl1665703025171__p_d94799e1_d94800e1_d94801e1\">Derived Entity specializes Entity in the following\n        ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"byl1665703025171__ul_hxp_3xp_lwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"byl1665703025171__li_d37160e1_d37161e1_d37162e1\">It inherits from a Modeled Entity.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"byl1665703025171__li_d37163e1_d37164e1_d37165e1\">It has a Modeled Entity, Component, or Modeled\n          Component as parent object.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612272\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612272\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Derived Entity Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 27, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Derived Entity A Derived Entity is a Development Object that references and inherits from a Modeled Entity. It can be a subobject of a Modeled Entity (in which case it is known as a Subtype Entity), or of a Component or Modeled Component. Characteristics Characteristic Icon: Object type code: ent Main Development Object? No Part of: Modeled Entity , Component , Modeled Component Contains: Field , Key , Relationship , Property , Code Container Generalization: Entity Specializations: Subtype Entity , Derived Component Entity Compilation Output: — URI format: ent: SupertypeEntityName /ent: SubtypeEntityName cpt: ComponentName /ent: EntityName Specialization Derived Entity specializes Entity in the following ways: It inherits from a Modeled Entity. It has a Modeled Entity, Component, or Modeled Component as parent object. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}